Al WILLIAMS and Al Williams Health System of Los Angeles, Inc., a Corporation, Appellants, v. Michael J. FANNING, Individually and as Postmaster of the City of Los Angeles, California, Appellee. No. 11317. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit Dec. 6, 1946. Richard L. North, of Los Angeles, Cal., for appellant. James M. Carter, U. S. Atty., and Ronald Walker and Clarke E. Stephens, Asst. U. S. Attys., all of Los Angeles, Cal., for appellee.

Before GARRECHT, DENMAN, and HEALY, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Upon the authority of Neher v. Har-wood, 9 Cir., 128 F.2d 846, 158 A.L.R. 1116, the judgment in this case is affirmed.
